Type of Feat: Class
Prerequisite: Tempest level 1.
Specifics: When wielding two weapons and wearing light or no armor, the Tempest gains the ability to defend herself with more skill and to seek out the gaps in an opponents defense.  The bonuses for a given level replace those of a previous level.
Level 1: +1 Dodge AC Bonus
Level 2: +1 Dodge AC Bonus, +1 Attack Bonus
Level 3: +2 Dodge AC Bonus, +1 Attack Bonus
Level 4: +2 Dodge AC Bonus, +2 Attack Bonus
Level 5: +3 Dodge AC Bonus, +2 Attack Bonus